						<div class="service-icon">
							<img src="/assets/WebsiteMarketing/InfraDev Assets/Estimate.png" alt="Tax Remittances" />
						</div>
						<h3>Tax Remittances</h3>
						<p>CPP, EI, QPP, QPIP remittances and T4/T4A tax slip generation.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="service-card">
						<div class="service-icon">
							<img src="/assets/WebsiteMarketing/InfraDev Assets/Architect.png" alt="Compliance" />
						</div>
						<h3>Labour Law Compliance</h3>
						<p>Provincial labour law compliance and workplace safety (CNESST).</p>
					</div>
					<div class="service-card">
						<div class="service-icon">
							<img src="/assets/WebsiteMarketing/InfraDev Assets/Discover.png" alt="Contracts" />
						</div>
						<h3>Employment Contracts</h3>
						<p>Legally compliant employment contracts and HR documentation.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="service-card">
						<div class="service-icon">
							<img src="/assets/WebsiteMarketing/InfraDev Assets/Launch.png" alt="Onboarding" />
						</div>
						<h3>Onboarding & Termination</h3>
						<p>Complete employee onboarding, time tracking, and termination processes including ROEs.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="service-card">
						<div class="service-icon">
							<img src="/assets/WebsiteMarketing/InfraDev Assets/Build.png" alt="Benefits" />
						</div>
						<h3>Benefits Administration</h3>
						<p>Optional benefits administration and HR support services.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Why U.S. Companies Use Us -->
		<section class="why-us section">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="section-header">
					<h2>Why U.S. Companies Use Us</h2>
					<p>Hiring in Canada normally requires forming a Canadian corporation, registering with the CRA, opening payroll accounts, and understanding provincial labour laws. With InfraDev, you skip all of this.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="benefits-grid">
					<div class="benefit-card">
						<div class="benefit-icon">‚ö°</div>
