					</div>
					<div class="benefit-card">
						<div class="benefit-icon">üõ°Ô∏è</div>
						<h3>Fully Compliant</h3>
						<p>Complete compliance with Canadian labour laws and regulations.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="benefit-card">
						<div class="benefit-icon">üìä</div>
						<h3>Transparent Billing</h3>
						<p>One simple monthly invoice - salary + employer contributions + service fee.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- How It Works -->
		<section id="how-it-works" class="how-it-works section">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="section-header">
					<h2>How It Works</h2>
					<p>A simple, streamlined process for cross-border hiring</p>
				</div>
				<div class="process-steps">
					<div class="process-step">
						<div class="step-number">1</div>
						<div class="process-icon">
							<img src="/assets/WebsiteMarketing/InfraDev Assets/Discover.png" alt="Select Candidate" />
						</div>
						<h3>You Select a Candidate</h3>
						<p>You choose the person you want to hire ‚Äî your employee or one we help you recruit.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="process-arrow">‚Üí</div>
					<div class="process-step">
						<div class="step-number">2</div>
						<div class="process-icon">
							<img src="/assets/WebsiteMarketing/InfraDev Assets/Build.png" alt="We Hire" />
						</div>
						<h3>We Hire Them in Canada</h3>
						<p>The worker becomes a legal employee of InfraDev Consulting under our Canadian company.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="process-arrow">‚Üí</div>
					<div class="process-step">
						<div class="step-number">3</div>
						<div class="process-icon">
							<img src="/assets/WebsiteMarketing/InfraDev Assets/Launch.png" alt="You Manage" />
						</div>
						<h3>You Manage Their Work</h3>
						<p>You assign tasks, evaluate performance, and integrate them into your team.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="process-arrow">‚Üí</div>
					<div class="process-step">
						<div class="step-number">4</div>
						<div class="process-icon">
							<img src="/assets/WebsiteMarketing/InfraDev Assets/Estimate.png" alt="Simple Invoice" />
						</div>
