						<ul class="pricing-list">
							<li>‚úì Gross salary of employee</li>
							<li>‚úì Employer contributions (CPP, EI, QPP, QPIP)</li>
							<li>‚úì Flat InfraDev EOR fee (starting at $XXX/month per employee)</li>
							<li>‚úì All payroll processing</li>
							<li>‚úì Tax remittances and compliance</li>
							<li>‚úì HR support and documentation</li>
						</ul>
